  "texts": [
    "The study was fully anonymous otherwise.",
    "A copy of the questionnaire is provided as Supplementary material.",
    "Here, we summarize its main items.",
    "For the items, participants could choose to select \"Prefer not to answer\" if they wish not to answer a question.",
    "For multiple choice questions, an additional option \"Other\" was provided in case participants wanted to specify an option that was not listed."
  ]
}